  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Face the invading Dark Wisp</h2>Play as the guardian Specter and his flying companion Mip as they travel deep into the depths to seal away the invading evil spirits known as the Dark Wisps, a group of ghostly apparitions who cause harm to the innocent creatures of the forest.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072030/extras/0e0dfba87b856ffa3febefe4c2b35232.poster.avif?t=1704851645\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072030/extras/0e0dfba87b856ffa3febefe4c2b35232.webm?t=1704851645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072030/extras/0e0dfba87b856ffa3febefe4c2b35232.mp4?t=1704851645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore an interconnected world as you fight your way against hordes of Ghostly Apparitions.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Switch between melee and ranged attacks as Specter and Mip. Slice your enemies as Specter & shoot enemies from a distance as Mip.</li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Get through tricky obstacles using Mip's Echolocation ability to reveal hidden platforms.</li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock new magic abilities for both Specter and Mip. Blow enemies into the wind with the tornado ability. Summon spectral swords that aid you in combat.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Obtain key items and solve light puzzles.</li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Inspect items you collected in your inventory.</li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Face hordes of Ghostly enemies and bosses.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Partial support for gamepad, & mouse + keyboard.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072030/extras/e842a3f6fc3ea6fd7d74bc74ba11515a.poster.avif?t=1704851645\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072030/extras/e842a3f6fc3ea6fd7d74bc74ba11515a.webm?t=1704851645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072030/extras/e842a3f6fc3ea6fd7d74bc74ba11515a.mp4?t=1704851645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
